# Tool: QueryTopExceptions
# Description: Query Application Insights for the top exceptions in the specified time range.
#   Use when investigating errors, exceptions, failures, or HTTP 5xx issues.
# Connector: Application Insights (ai-sre-demo)
# Parameters:
#   - timeRange (string): How far back to look (e.g. 1h, 24h, 7d)
#   - limit (int): Max results to return (default: 10)

exceptions
| where timestamp > ago(##timeRange##)
| summarize
    count() as occurrence_count,
    latest_timestamp = max(timestamp),
    earliest_timestamp = min(timestamp)
  by type, outerMessage, problemId
| order by occurrence_count desc
| take ##limit##
